782
00:43:34,820 --> 00:43:36,680
People don't even seem to welcome me here.

783
00:43:40,460 --> 00:43:41,400
But it's not such a surprise.

784
00:43:42,100 --> 00:43:44,180
I caused so much trouble for everyone.

785
00:43:46,930 --> 00:43:48,130
I can't even do anything.

786
00:43:49,430 --> 00:43:50,890
It doesn't come as a surprise...

787
00:43:51,500 --> 00:43:52,780
