together for a long time.

812
00:45:58,100 --> 00:45:59,280
Saitharn!

813
00:45:59,830 --> 00:46:01,330
Auntie Nong asked me to take you to eat!

814
00:46:01,380 --> 00:46:02,760
You haven't eaten anything, have you?!

815
00:46:02,860 --> 00:46:03,680
Saitharn?!

